# Bayesian Spam Detector

**Live Naïve Bayes Spam Filter** built from scratch with Flask + Python.

**Assignment**: MAT-2226 Engineering Mathematics-IV Seminar (Group 1)

### Features
- Real SMS Spam Collection dataset (UCI)
- From-scratch Naïve Bayes with Laplace smoothing
- Unbiased priors (P(Spam) = P(Ham) = 0.5)
- Log-space calculation + visible posterior probability
- Beautiful blackboard-themed UI
- Full math transparency ("Show Math" panel)
- 80/20 train-test split + evaluation metrics

### How to Run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py